{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Frenzy VR is an action fighter all about destruction &amp; interactive environments. </h2>You can use **any object** as a weapon with our advanced destruction physics for realistic mayhem. Frenzy VR includes a **story mode** with deep narrative secrets, levels, and objectives. Take the chaos into your own hands with **free play modes** allowing unlimited creativity across **various maps** like offices, apartments, prisons, and more.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/METALINE.png?t=1726777017\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FULLY INTERACTIVE AND DESTRUCTIBLE WORLDS</strong></h2>All maps feature fully destructible items, objects, &amp; enemies<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/v1-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1726777017\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>RAGDOLL PHYSICS WITH MELEE / RANGED WEAPONS</strong></h2>NPCs use realistic physics ragdolls for ultimate chaos and mayhem<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/v2-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1726777017\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>STORY MODE WITH NARRATIVE AND CAMPAIGN</strong></h2>Complete the full story with multiple missions and take down the Reborn Company<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/v3-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1726777017\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>10+ REALISTIC MAPS AND MISSIONS</strong></h2>Go ballistic in fully interactable worlds built specifically for you to destroy <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/v4-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1726777017\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FULL WEAPON CUSTOMIZATION AND UPGRADES</strong></